{"tid":306204,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角同九龍城中間既地方叫咩名？","createTime":"2017-07-02T10:35:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-03T07:16:50.000Z","uid":75868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"79881480dd6bb51a5abe80226cc05b6e490544b2","tid":306204,"uid":75868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:35:40.000Z","msg":"今日搭車經過太子道西諗到呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31042924f3e5e85016d1a1668d8f6df37e942d20","tid":306204,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:36:21.000Z","msg":"九龍塘"},{"pid":"421121ced3482ce4f1a097a9a2f91781c3515113","tid":306204,"uid":45749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:36:36.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣"},{"pid":"ba7d0d25429f44cd0396baa846c6a1fa0d6f0349","tid":306204,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:37:02.000Z","msg":"九龍塘? 九龍仔?"},{"pid":"9e615e396d0e9af4a0942b58245b5124f6101a47","tid":306204,"uid":54593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:37:38.000Z","msg":"九龍塘"},{"pid":"b39bfbb9cf9086406c9a60fdd828834a457b0758","tid":306204,"uid":66026,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:41:00.000Z","msg":"咪就係太子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac430e6eecaafecc4bf30ac75555aa3c63267500","tid":306204,"uid":117302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:52:17.000Z","msg":"何文田？"},{"pid":"949acffa6683818730434fb98cb06f3c5776af75","tid":306204,"uid":125655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T10:58:25.000Z","msg":"九龍角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3008b9f93f12dcc8f389ce6d35851b0cf69627","tid":306204,"uid":35505,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:02:41.000Z","msg":"由九龍城一直到法國醫院一帶都係九龍城<br />\n九龍城至太子一帶北面係九龍仔<br />\n南面係加多利山同何文田"},{"pid":"f6d87b6e71e2a233546756f5fa0b050f590ef7ac","tid":306204,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:06:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>九龍角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n九龍角是香港昔日海角，指九龍尖沙咀天星碼頭及海運大廈一帶。一般而言，這個地名現在很少人用，一般將其視為尖沙咀的一個部份。<br />\n<br />\n其對出的海域，曾是九龍角填海計劃的地點，該區日後亦會稱為九龍角。然而，由於香港不少人士反對填海工程，結果該計劃被逼擱置[1][2]。"},{"pid":"60a4312715ea977f5a05788bcb9a89c2288038e4","tid":306204,"uid":38099,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:10:31.000Z","msg":"法國醫院開始就九龍塘<br />\n到界限街後就太子<br />\n利申:住太子道西"},{"pid":"ad66fbd7dfc32c470e10f6982d06160a6b0c0471","tid":306204,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T11:16:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>法國醫院開始就九龍塘<br />\n到界限街後就太子<br />\n利申:住太子道西</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過左九龍仔即係延文禮士道之後先係九龍塘"},{"pid":"e0ca83c5edeab0b3d610a69d81d67c2de7fc28b5","tid":306204,"uid":38099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T12:14:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>法國醫院開始就九龍塘<br />\n到界限街後就太子<br />\n利申:住太子道西</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n過左九龍仔即係延文禮士道之後先係九龍塘</blockquote><br />\n過嘉林邊道就算(好似)"},{"pid":"7a4da15519ff5408b135ec892044a6c258e35461","tid":306204,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"九龍城區嘅嘉道理選區（G07）及太子選區（G08）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cdcc018df9ddce0147471247fc5641696c480d1","tid":306204,"uid":125655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T07:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>九龍角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n九龍角是香港昔日海角，指九龍尖沙咀天星碼頭及海運大廈一帶。一般而言，這個地名現在很少人用，一般將其視為尖沙咀的一個部份。<br />\n<br />\n其對出的海域，曾是九龍角填海計劃的地點，該區日後亦會稱為九龍角。然而，由於香港不少人士反對填海工程，結果該計劃被逼擱置[1][2]。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係有韃咁既地"}]}